{"type": "article", "id": 14113, "title": "小型阳台休息处组合", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-28T07:27:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060600340928bAjgwVhocWvrtI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t巴塞罗那设计师 Pola Clapés 设计了一个小型的阳台休息处，一个支架上包括五种产品，分别是一个植物悬挂处，一个晾衣架和三个尺寸不一的小桌子，如果原本有一个空荡的阳台，可以选择用它来更好地利用空间。这是设计师的个人主页，<a href=\"http://cargocollective.com/polaclapes\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看他的更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141735xm0oVaWFdJvcpeBr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261417369mnXwfVFdlNZyIcM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141737boGHxMwmCZnEfTlB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05012225\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261417373YjNf2sdxl17HWm8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70904645\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141738HYF04uQ197OMWcp2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00855746\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}